snippet.title: Vampire Survivors: Emerald Diorama | Launch Trailer | OUT NOW
snippet.description:
Become a Showstopper of SaGa legend in Vampire Survivors: Emerald Diorama!

Our first FREE expansion for Vampire Survivors, based on Square Enix’s hit franchise SaGa, is available today on Steam, Xbox, PlayStation 4/5, Nintendo Switch, Epic, Android & iOS.

With 12+ new characters, 16+ new weapons (including a new Glimmer mechanic), a World-Weaving Stage, a bunch of new remixes, and so much more to discover - are you ready to step into the unknown?

Vampire Survivors by poncle
© SQUARE ENIX
